{"tid":1476112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民真係天生鍾意玩割席","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T10:04:44.000Z","uid":28068,"like":11,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1e789bf047f5f9161ac4073cea0dcac5bfae07f9","tid":1476112,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"以前割勇武 割本土<br />\n依家就連trump都想割<br />\n有本事你咪自己搞掂晒d野囉<br />\n無既唔該縮番埋啦"},{"pid":"905c863287fec72e77d222637e39961275420c03","tid":1476112,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"分析大家可以點應對818反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475432</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n入黎傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多巴絲對818有諗法！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n總括post入邊大家意見：<br />\n818不衝 不圍 不挑釁 不設防 能放能收 坐爆維園<br />\n<br />\n有手足提出：<br />\n<br />\n1.唔佔馬路 齋坐行人路（坐行人路唔係非法集會？有冇法律手足講下）<br />\n<br />\n2.記得戴定口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同頭盔或帽，保護自己<br />\n<br />\n3.如果有人行跡可疑 就示威者手鏈圍大圈 圈入面就記者同幾位勇d嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果冇野大家唔會驚 如果有野就制服佢 搵證據 俾記者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 維園冇位就坐係沿途商埸 一齊睇live 順便幫人哋罷市<br />\n<br />\n5. 避開坐爆之前同黑社會發生衝突嘅位置，避免引起衝突，恐慌<br />\n<br />\n6. 無論所有交通工具都金鐘落，行去維園，行唔到就坐<br />\n<br />\n7. 64當年有軍火隨街放，大家記住唔好拎同點！唔好俾藉囗中共鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n8. -出得嚟就要同自己打定最壞打算，無論咩人都係<br />\n-要克服你嘅恐慌 有突發事出現，<br />\n同隔離嗰個一齊分擔<br />\n-唔好因爲緊張亂講野，唔好因爲緊張亂信人<br />\n9.夠鐘就散場 下次再遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n試下說 勇武手法/和理非手法<br />\n任何手足都可以唔同場合，用唔同手法做事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199e408659e464f9b51b2f4f27ca463af34f7493","tid":1476112,"uid":153781,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"收皮la 分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ffcf28c894ec7b74754f56aef2beb3cab73432","tid":1476112,"uid":264457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"6f6ea46353c1437fa2a8cd0394c944f8f479b09b","tid":1476112,"uid":38572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"分化撚"},{"pid":"6404c0b0ad1baaa4735bd60331d1034fac447df2","tid":1476112,"uid":92340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"hocc又係泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c273b5f480a7e97fa7b3787efdc4845713b871","tid":1476112,"uid":37600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n就算割蓆都唔撚割呀"},{"pid":"f0215b5f6fed65270b7e13a0e55863199cb4655c","tid":1476112,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38c273b5f480a7e97fa7b3787efdc4845713b871","tid":1476112,"uid":37600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n就算割蓆都唔撚割呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"On9不分化唔係咁解"},{"pid":"ba61b9a5099c1878950fd6a3cde56558443b4c63","tid":1476112,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"錯就係錯 你班友班性少少ok?"},{"pid":"4c57fee59f846cd6b052022f717105cbdd45b067","tid":1476112,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba61b9a5099c1878950fd6a3cde56558443b4c63","tid":1476112,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"錯就係錯 你班友班性少少ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"理性"},{"pid":"2a6d40a0effedaf08eb39553ffcda